description: A list of documents attached to an index.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the application id the documents are attached to.

parameters.name: indexId
parameters.description: The identifier of the index the documents are attached to.

parameters.name: dataSourceIds
parameters.description: The identifier of the data sources the documents are attached to. (string) ---

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current status of the document.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: The message explaining the Amazon Q Business request error.

nested_items.name: errorCode
nested_items.description: The code associated with the Amazon Q Business request error.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the document was created.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the document was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the maxResults response was incomplete because there is more data to retrieve, Amazon Q Business returns a pagination token in the response. You can use this pagination token to retrieve the next set of documents.
